"  bobgui4-image-tool [COMMAND] [OPTION…] FILE…\n"
"\n"
"Perform various tasks on images.\n"
"\n"
"Commands:\n"
"  compare      Show differences between two images\n"
"  convert      Convert the image to a different format or color state\n"
